header.name: Extra Chests
header.description: Extra Chests Pack [BP]. It's a new Minecraft chests addon for pocket, Desktop and console Edition. It support only 1.19.30 and above. Every chest have it's unique UI Texture and custom open & close animation with sounds. It contain Copper, Iron, Gold, Emerald, Diamond, Netherite chests.All chests are lockable and can be breaked wth custom items using a random chance.
